text: Andres Tarand (born 11 January 1940) is an Estonian politician. He was the Prime Minister of Estonia from 1994 to 1995. He was also a Member of the European Parliament (MEP) for the Social Democratic Party, part of the Party of European Socialists, between 2004 and 2009. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Estonia Category:Politicians from Tallinn Category:MEPs for Estonia
